1 WHEREAS, Louisiana and its political subdivisions should seek to aid
2 Transportation Security Administration agents during this time of uncertainty by providing
3 temporary financial assistance.
4 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Legislature of Louisiana does hereby
5 urge and request the city of Shreveport to create an interest-free loan program for active
6 Transportation Security Administration agents at the Shreveport Regional Airport.
7 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
8 mayor of the city of Shreveport, the city council of the city of Shreveport, and the Caddo
9 Parish Commission.
